column2: Symptom
I have a terrible stomach ache and diarrhea.
My chest feels tight and I'm having trouble breathing.
I feel dizzy, nauseous, and I think I have a fever.
Frequent urination with a burning sensation.
I have acid reflux and a burning feeling in my chest (heartburn).
My blood pressure is very high and my neck feels stiff.
I'm constantly thirsty, drinking lots of water but losing weight.
My heart is beating very fast (palpitations) and I feel uncomfortable.
I look pale and feel dizzy whenever I stand up (anemia).
I haven't been able to sleep for days (insomnia) and feel exhausted.
I cut my hand deeply while slicing fruit and it's bleeding heavily.
I fell on my knee, it's swollen and I can't walk.
I got burned by hot water, my skin is red and blistering.
I was in a bike accident and have road rash with debris in the wound.
I have hemorrhoids and it hurts when I sit down.
I think I dislocated my shoulder, I can't raise my arm.
Severe pain in my lower right abdomen, looking like appendicitis.
I was bitten by a stray dog on my leg and it's bleeding.
I have a growing lump (cyst) on my back.
I have an ingrown toenail that is infected and painful.
I have a severe sore throat, it feels like razor blades when I swallow.
My nose is running constantly and I keep sneezing (allergies).
I feel like there's a bug buzzing inside my ear.
I lost my voice and sound very hoarse.
My tonsils are swollen and painful.
I have a nosebleed that won't stop.
Everything is spinning (vertigo) and I feel like vomiting.
My ear feels blocked and I can't hear clearly.
I accidentally swallowed a fish bone and it's stuck in my throat.
I have painful mouth ulcers (canker sores) and can't eat.
I have a lot of acne on my face and want treatment.
I have a red, itchy rash all over my back.
I have a corn on the bottom of my foot that hurts when I walk.
I have severe dandruff and an itchy scalp.
My fingernails are turning grey and thick (fungal infection).
I broke out in hives all over my body and it's extremely itchy.
I'm losing a lot of hair recently, there's a bald spot.
I have a hard wart on the sole of my foot.
I got a bad sunburn at the beach, my back is peeling and painful.
A mole on my body is changing shape and growing bigger.
My eyes are very red and have a lot of discharge.
My vision is blurry and I see dark shadows.
My eyes feel dry, gritty, and irritated.
I have a stye on my eyelid and it's swollen.
I feel like my nearsightedness has gotten worse, I can't see clearly.
My contact lens is stuck and my eye hurts.
I see floating spots (floaters) moving in my vision.
My eyes feel very pressured and sore, with a headache.
The white part of my eye is bleeding (red patch).
Straight lines look wavy and distorted to me.
